7dac6ff36b0bee0a215df819b4","tid":61691,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f89a5f6f4ac090aaf6688f5e8bd27abe0ce383c2","tid":61691,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死"},{"pid":"ba45273796d91a698bfc44a42363e15720f67a13","tid":61691,"uid":2581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太陽呢"},{"pid":"693047c608b180e3237aa3e20098e09d787aa514","tid":61691,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太陽呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係放左係窗邊 得唔得"},{"pid":"21bc09f05d11b80dd6df57dd9c8a022e7d615b50","tid":61691,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32324c605ab725c10a6115ad2e4c4ceffd8f6e97","tid":61691,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無暖管<br />\n無filter<br />\n一星期換一次水<br />\n加隻燈<br />\n係咁多，仲幾生猛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一日換兩次係咪唔係咁好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ff16dd33ee1a24068dc47545b58eef7a2c2b9d","tid":61691,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:59:52.000Z","msg":"未研究清楚就唔好養啦，害死啲小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa156112c2ce3935fdce8c254303bce9b8bd130","tid":61691,"uid":29371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"養咗兩年半 依家兩隻龜都大過我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388da93c4a583e50c6ba2c74d95b654ec5699a09","tid":61691,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:03:47.000Z","msg":"自來水水質有問題？巴西龜好粗生喎"},{"pid":"462cc4f6bfabe05f9d5fb1199c561c43e39ac77e","tid":61691,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未研究清楚就唔好養啦，害死啲小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾返啲🐢人啦"},{"pid":"53be9e70a9dfbbf92208634594f0b1c7505af110","tid":61691,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a82e217a09691415640af94acedabb37c9ddb9d","tid":61691,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:12:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6e86c1eab7481356a585fcb44516bf43b4ce599","tid":61691,"uid":70774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該有關環境問題，如果長期係水中都會有水腫死，要設有一個area俾佢可以陸水都有得選擇，溫度都有關系"},{"pid":"a1f1a36c8c2d0f365cc56e2e0d53b33d273a2cba","tid":61691,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:13:32.000Z","msg":"做下好心放過佢地一條生路唔好再養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d9ae15cbbe3b8ecc8ec011b4704534f5a5ace","tid":61691,"uid":42082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該有關環境問題，如果長期係水中都會有水腫死，要設有一個area俾佢可以陸水都有得選擇，溫度都有關系</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n系你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番去讀完小學先上黎啦"},{"pid":"437ab3ec10bd9edaa7aba1fa99d2702d58d9a784","tid":61691,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無暖管<br />\n無filter<br />\n一星期換一次水<br />\n加隻燈<br />\n係咁多，仲幾生猛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一日換兩次係咪唔係咁好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個缸幾大？一日兩次咪好攰？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個缸唔係好大，又唔高<br />\n有隻龜唔知點解愈養愈大，行兩步游兩下就到另一邊，其餘兩隻完全冇變過size，仲係好細隻<br />\n唔攰但好煩，餵之前一次，餵之後一次"},{"pid":"5a061b04ddf8e8c276cadee4806468aae48e31d3","tid":61691,"uid":70774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該有關環境問題，如果長期係水中都會有水腫死，要設有一個area俾佢可以陸水都有得選擇，溫度都有關系</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n系你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番去讀完小學先上黎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇咩suggestion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a135a20a74eb376fc0090a4887ced792d261cf79","tid":61691,"uid":61133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴西龜 明明已經有水喂野食 但係成日無啦啦死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太陽呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係放左係窗邊 得唔得</blockquote><br />\n巴打 窗嘅玻璃會折射陽光入面唔同頻率嘅光線 仲會令到UV-B變得好弱 咁隻龜哂唔夠 UV-B自然身體唔好 易病 易軟殼<br />\n最好就買返一盞UV-B 燈 幾百蚊有一把 跟返日照時間照佢 同埋記住要留意龜嘅殼同外露皮膚嘅軟硬變化 有冇突然有白色直紋，裂紋。 總之唔清楚就要搵獸醫，有啲錢唔慳得。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 獸醫助理"},{"pid":"ee680fdf2ed0ab051387f73f6ebefc43d9998294","tid":61691,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdqptc7fmKHfBP2jSK9wRYBj4Pjgqzip3hQ1tvtcYxC62?filename=29WhqbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29WhqbL.jpg&h=283287de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPMaVJMWAznLL5HEdFj5Jxgr9NvqmZbLMM9vM5Rrg3fv7?filename=4fun6hH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fun6hH.jpg&h=8fb739b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/01/032652_cda65d2736dafaf95634906ca1e676ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F01%2F032652_cda65d2736dafaf95634906ca1e676ed.jpg&h=30aac1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養左9年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e5518670de931211518eab40a199b277ba62ce","tid":61691,"uid":70659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未研究清楚就唔好養啦，害死啲小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾返啲🐢人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}